      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "貴方と麻奈の、本当の始まりの場所よ\nこのステージでも、あの駅前でもないんでしょ？",
      "startTime": 248.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
