      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の席は、あそこでした。ほら、後ろの\n俺の席は……その隣でした",
