      "text": "それに、もっと知りたかったのは本当よ\n私の知らない彼女と、私の知らない……",
      "startTime": 324.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio036.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん。それは別にいいの\nありがとう。とても参考になったわ",
      "startTime": 332.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……莉央さんは\n麻奈の次に俺を振り回すアイドルですよ",
      "startTime": 337.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_05_02-rio037.m4a",
      "text": "そう。じゃあこれからはもっと振り回して\n一番にならなきゃね",
      "startTime": 344.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
